Third Department,

August, 1973

(August 1, 1973) The People of the State of New York ex rel. Harry W. Yates, Petitioner, v. Joseph Wasser, as Sheriff of Sullivan County, New York, Respondent.

Application, pursuant to CPLR 7002 (subd. [b], par; 2), for a writ of habeas corpus denied for failure of compliance with article 70 of theCPLR and more particularly with the provisions of CPLR 7002 (subd. [c]) .thereof, and as otherwise insufficient on its face. Greenblott, J. P., Cooke, Sweeney, Kane and Reynolds, JJ., concur.
